{"tid":209147,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣被拍到海邊獨自踱步拭淚惹起網路揣測","createTime":"2017-04-20T03:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T01:43:54.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc4f9fb76692c0d82039cd9f7f4a20889f16706","tid":209147,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"日本甜心新垣結衣演出日劇《月薪嬌妻》，成為國民老婆，清新自然的形象深植人心，代言接到手軟，茶飲、服飾等都能看見她的身影。而日前她為國民品牌衛生紙拍攝的代言廣告公開，流著眼淚的嬌嫩模樣，讓觀眾超揪心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n35V25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn35V25.png&h=a15935c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣告的背景是在海邊，並以拉遠的鏡頭，逐漸靠近新垣結衣，沒想到新垣結衣一回頭眼淚就像是珍珠般不斷落下，搭配用鋼琴彈奏的輕音樂，觀眾邊看都覺得揪心，而她用衛生紙擦拭後，才說出廣告詞，讓看呆的眾人恍然大悟，原來是新垣結衣代言的新廣告！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2TJFUL8QY5M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2TJFUL8QY5M&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=e3bddb22\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2TJFUL8QY5M</a><br />\n▲新垣結衣在拍攝的廣告中落淚的模樣，讓人看了超揪心。"},{"pid":"cdf4367497225817d308b163b360aca1ab2a0fab","tid":209147,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef113fc401e5469c8527c4bb70647acc7f46725","tid":209147,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6a198165e8e500cf295a1a4fce322b1a1a17055","tid":209147,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7f9ffbfa18058afb512efad01a8b60809d320e","tid":209147,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:12:56.000Z","msg":"護駕！"},{"pid":"1b013b03bd58b16409ec0af53ac1f0a38e6477a1","tid":209147,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"又有朱